All 3D measurements were conducted using ImageJ (version 1.48; [36]). Leaf disc porosity, the number of individual air channels, the porosity distribution through the leaf disc depth, and the surface area of mesophyll cells exposed to intercellular airspace (Smes) were all calculated from data acquired using the ImageJ function ‘Analyze Particles’. Leaf porosity (%) was calculated using Eq. 1:1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
